<section.block>
<section>
<section.front>
<outline.name.block>
<designator>32:12</designator>
<name>Checklist-- Information required in certificate of incorporation of agricultural cooperative corporation</name>
</outline.name.block>
</section.front>
<section.body>
<online.view.item>FTR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>COR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>EBL</online.view.item>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
1. Name of corporation, which must include word &ldquo;“Cooperative.&rdquo;”
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
2. Statement of purpose or purposes for which cooperative is formed, which shall be one or more of <trace>the </trace>objects enumerated in the N.Y. Cooperative Corporations Law.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
3. City, village or town and county in which its office is to be located.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
4. Term of existence of corporation.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
5. Names and post office addresses of incorporators.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
6. Statement of whether organized with or without capital stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
7. If organized with capital stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
a. Statement of total authorized capital stock, number and types of shares, and par value of shares.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
b. Rights, preferences, and restrictions of each type of share.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
c. If preferred stock is issued, a limitation on dividends that will not exceed 12&percnt;% per year.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
8. Number of its directors or that number of directors will be within a stated minimum and maximum as stated in bylaws. In any event, number may not be less than five.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
9. Names and post office addresses of directors until first annual meeting.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
10. Statement that all subscribers are of full age, that at least two-thirds of them are citizens of the United States, that at least one of them is a resident of New York, and that of the persons named as directors at least one is a citizen of the United States and a resident of the State of New York.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
11. Designation of Secretary of State as agent of corporation upon whom process may be served and post office address within or without New York to which Secretary of State may mail a copy of any process against it served on such official.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
12. If corporation is to have a registered agent, his or her name and address within New York and a statement that the registered agent is to be the agent of the corporation upon whom process against it may be served.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
13. Any other provision(s) consistent with law with respect to management, regulation, government, financing, indebtedness, membership, issuance, retirement, and transfer of stock, if required, or any provisions relative to way or manner in which cooperative corporation will operate or with respect to its members, officers, or directors and any other provisions relating to its affairs.
</para.text>
</para>
<trace.deleted>Drafter's Note</trace.deleted>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|12|32:12">
<para.text>
See ►<field>st.ref.id="I05RVNJ"</field>Coop. Corp. Law &s;§11 for discussion of the required contents of the certificate.
</para.text>
</para>
