<section.block>
<section>
<section.front>
<outline.name.block>
<designator>32:13</designator>
<name>Checklist-- Matters that may be covered in bylaws of agricultural cooperative</name>
</outline.name.block>
</section.front>
<section.body>
<online.view.item>FCV</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>FTR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>EBL</online.view.item>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
1. Name of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Principal office.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Other offices.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
2. Purposes and objectives of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Method of accomplishing.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) In accordance with all laws and regulations.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) In compliance with requirements of the Internal Revenue Code to qualify for cooperative status.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
Business with nonmembers shall not exceed business done with members.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
3. Membership.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Eligibility for membership or to purchase stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Method of joining.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Application.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) Registration fee.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(3) Subscription for membership or stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(A) Installment payments.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
Interest payable.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(B) Full payment.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(C) Patronage payments, dividends, and other refunds credited to member as payment on share or stock until fully paid.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(4) Approval of board of directors.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) Voting rights per membership share or shares of stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(d) Payment of patronage dividends and other distributions made on basis of membership share.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) All payments in compliance with Internal Revenue Code.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) Payments made in cash unless member directs payment to purchase of additional shares.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(A) Limitation on number of membership shares or shares of stock.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(B) Suspension and removal of members.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(i) Grounds.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(ii) Procedure.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(e) Membership interests and stock not transferable.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Exception for transfers to family members.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
Approval of board of directors.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(f) Membership shares and stock are nonassessable.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
4. Withdrawal of amounts credited on purchase of membership or stock shares.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Withdrawal upon written request.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Cooperative has until one year from date of request to pay.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) Payment in cash, goods, or services of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(d) Partial withdrawal to result in proportionate reduction of credits and distributions.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
5. Distributions.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Patronage refunds based on purchases.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Dividends on capital limited to greater of 8&percnt;% or legal rate of interest.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) Any capital impairment restored before distributions are made.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(d) Payment of earnings of cooperative based on purchases and business done with cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
6. Each member to include patronage dividends and other distributions in income in accordance with Internal Revenue Code.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
7. Meetings of members.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Annual meeting.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Purposes.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) Date, time, location.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(3) Notices.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Special meetings.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Method for calling.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) Purpose.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(3) Notices.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) Quorum for meetings.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(d) Conduct of meeting.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(e) Proxies.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(f) Method of voting.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
8. Directors.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Number (not less than five), tenure, qualifications.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Member of cooperative in good standing.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(b) Time and manner of nominating and choosing.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(c) Qualifications.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(d) Term of office.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(e) Election at annual meeting.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(f) Number, not less than a majority, needed to exercise their powers.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(g) Powers and duties.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(h) Prohibition of self-dealing.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(i) Compensation.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(j) Method for removing director.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) Grounds for removal.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) Procedure.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(k) Meetings of directors.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
Regular meetings.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
9. Officers.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(a) Titles.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(1) President (appointed from directors).
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(2) One or more vice presidents (appointed from directors).
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
(3) Secretary and treasurer, or secretary-treasurer (need not be directors or members, but must be elected by members).
