<online.view.item>Item 16(a).</online.view.item>
<trace.deleted>Drafter's Note</trace.deleted>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|13|32:13">
<para.text>
Before handling funds or securities of the corporation, amounting to $1,000 or more in any one year, the officer or employee shall be covered by an adequate bond to be approved by the board of directors. ►<field>st.ref.id="I05P1XD"</field>Coop. Corp. Law &s;§65.
</para.text>
</para>
