►<field>entry.nameend="5"</field><field>entry.namest="2"</field><field>entry.resize="same"</field><field>entry.style="block"</field>11. How will the Board of Directors be chosen? On the basis of size of business, by districts, at large, or a combination? What fees and expenses will be paid to Directors?
