►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|16|32:16">
<para.text>
This and other revolving fund certificates of the same series may be retired in the sole discretion of the board of directors, either fully or on a pro rata basis, but certificates issued in prior years will be entitled to priority (except as provided in this document) in retirement.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>2.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|16|32:16">
<para.text>
The amount stated in this certificate will bear only such rate of interest, if any, as the board of directors may fix, from time to time, in no event to exceed [percentage rate of annual interest]&percnt;% per year.
