►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|16|32:16">
<para.text>
This certificate is transferable only on the books of the corporation.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>4.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|16|32:16">
<para.text>
This and other certificates are subject in all respects to the corporation's bylaws and are junior and subordinate to all debts of the corporation, both secured and unsecured.
