►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|16|32:16">
<para.text>
Upon the winding up or liquidation of the corporation in any manner, after full payment of all of its creditors, all revolving fund certificates will then be retired in full or on a pro rata basis, without priority.
