►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>CERTIFICATE OF INCORPORATION OF [NAME OF CORPORATION]
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|17|32:17">
<para.text>
We, the undersigned, [names of persons engaged in production of agricultural products], have voluntarily associated ourselves together for the purpose of forming a nonprofit agricultural cooperative corporation under and by virtue of the laws of the State of New York and particularly under the provisions of Chapter 77, Article 6 of the Consolidated Laws of the State of New York and certify to the following:
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="2"</field>ARTICLE I  NAME
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|17|32:17">
<para.text>
The name of this corporation shall be [name of corporation].
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="2"</field>ARTICLE II  PURPOSE
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|17|32:17">
<para.text>
The purpose for which the corporation is formed is [description of purpose for incorporation].
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="2"</field>ARTICLE III  TERRITORY AND PRINCIPAL OFFICE
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|17|32:17">
<para.text>
