►<field>form.du="0"</field><field>form.fid="Ia3942470181a11e68738d3db3a7c8dd3"</field>►<field>p.ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19"</field>The purposes for which this organization is formed are:
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>(1).
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19">
<para.text>
to associate its members together for their mutual benefit as growers of [description of product];
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>(2).
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19">
<para.text>
to assist its members without profit to the Corporation in promoting the demand for and sale of [description of product 1] and [description of product 2] through advertising and promotional work with processors, handlers, consumers, and others;
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>(3).
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19">
<para.text>
to provide its members with marketing information to represent its members' point of view to state and federal agencies, to buyers, and to the public;
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>(4).
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19">
<para.text>
to cooperate with similar associations or agencies in performing any of the purposes for which that association is formed; and
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>(5).
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|19|32:19">
<para.text>
to perform any and all things not inconsistent with law that affect the mutual interests of [description of product] growers.
</para.text>
</para>
<online.view.item>Notes to Form</online.view.item>
