<trace.deleted> ►p.ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|26|32:26"(iii) For purposes of this paragraph, &ldquo;“reasonable measures&rdquo;” with respect to participating in proceedings shall include, but not be limited to, audio webcast or other broadcast of the meeting and for voting shall include but not be limited to telephonic and internet voting.</trace.deleted>
