<online.view.item>COR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>TEM</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>MTD</online.view.item>
►<field>form.du="0"</field><field>form.fid="Ia3990670181a11e68738d3db3a7c8dd3"</field>►<field>p.ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|34|32:33"</field>The Board of Directors may repurchase at par value, plus any declared and unpaid dividends, the common capital stock of any deceased member. Should the Cooperative not desire to repurchase such stock of a deceased member it may be sold or transferred to any other person eligible for membership in the Corporation as set forth in these bylaws.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|34|32:33">
<para.text>
The board of directors shall not buy the member's stock for more than par value.
</para.text>
</para>
