<section.block>
<section>
<section.front>
<outline.name.block>
<designator>32:50</designator>
<name>Checklist-- Matters to consider when drafting a marketing contract</name>
</outline.name.block>
</section.front>
<section.body>
<online.view.item>FTR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>COR</online.view.item>
<online.view.item>EBL</online.view.item>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
1. Names and addresses of parties.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
2. Produce covered.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Description.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Grade.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Prior encumbrances.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(d) Government standards to be met.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(e) Other specifications.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(f) Quantity.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(1) Entire production.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
Exclude home consumption.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(2) Stated amount.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
3. Sale to cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Term of contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(1) Stated period.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(2) Growing season.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Right of parties to earlier termination.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
4. Delivery of produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Place and time.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Inspection.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
Right of cooperative to reject.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Passage of title.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
5. Obligations of producer.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Produce maximum quantity of merchantable produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Notify cooperative of produce planted and harvested.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Pay for cooperative's services.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
As set by cooperative from time to time.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(d) Abide by terms of articles of incorporation, bylaws, and regulations of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
Right of cooperative to amend from time to time.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(e) Warranties of producer.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(1) Right to enter into contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(2) Produce will be delivered in accordance to specifications free of liens and encumbrances.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
6. Obligations of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Market produce at best price.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Inspect, grade, pack, ship produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Advertise produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(d) Pay producer for produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(1) Manner of establishing purchase price.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(2) Advances to producer.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(e) Distribute surplus to producers.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
Pro rata on basis of produce delivered.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
7. Rights of cooperative.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Sell output of other members and commingle produce.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Hold produce for next selling season.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Treat produce of producers in different ways.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(d) Prorate services among members if facilities not sufficient.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
8. Remedies for breach of contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Liquidated damages.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Injunctive relief.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Specific performance.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
9. General.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(a) Entire agreement between parties.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(b) Binding on heirs, successors, and assigns.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(c) Right of assignment of contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(d) Incorporation of articles of incorporation, bylaws, and regulations into contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(e) Legal expenses and attorney's fees.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(f) Date of contract.
</para.text>
</para>
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|52|32:50">
<para.text>
(g) Signatures.
</para.text>
</para>
