►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
All products will be delivered by producer at the earliest reasonable time when ready and, in any event, prior to the [ordinal number of day] day of [name of month] in each year, as and where directed by corporation. Where the packing plants of the corporation or its subsidiary are distant from the common delivery point, corporation may, in its discretion, assume the cost of transportation from the common shipping point to its packing plant. However, the delivery will not be deemed to have been made under this agreement except at the plant or grading points designated by corporation.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>b.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
Any deduction, charge, or loss that corporation may make or suffer because of inferior grade, quality, or condition of products will be charged against the producer individually.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>c.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
Corporation will make rules and regulations regarding handling and delivering and will provide inspectors and graders to standardize, grade, and classify products; producer agrees to observe and to perform any such rules and regulations and to accept the grading and standards established by corporation.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>d.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
All products will be delivered in merchantable condition. The corporation's determination as to grade, standard, and classification and differentials in prices will be conclusive.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>e.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
All products delivered under this agreement will be produced in compliance with the requirements of the Fair Labor Standards Act, as amended, and all regulations and orders of the U.S. Department of Labor issued thereunder, and with the requirements of any applicable New York authority or other applicable acts and all regulations and orders issued thereunder.
</para.text>
</para>
►<field>fi.lvl="1"</field>f.
►<para ct.id="6d0bf250b92611ef8747b569df12a67d|56|32:54">
<para.text>
Producer guarantees all products, deliverable under this contract as of the date of shipment or delivery to be on such date, not adulterated or misbranded within the meaning of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act and not an article that may not, under the provisions of the Act (as the same now exists or may hereafter be amended), be introduced into interstate commerce.
</para.text>
</para>
